videos.description: James Blackmon Jr. air-balls the 3-pointer but Juwan Morgan gets the offensive rebound for the easy layup as Indiana leads Ohio State.
videos.headline: Everything going Indiana's way early

videos.description: Thomas Bryant spins around the defender and makes the tough up and under shot to extend Indiana's lead over Ohio State.
videos.headline: Indiana's Bryant gets free with spin move

videos.description: Indiana's Josh Newkirk beats the defender with the crossover and then fights through the contact for the layup against Ohio State.
videos.headline: Indiana's Newkirk crosses over defender for and-1 layup

videos.description: Indiana's Josh Newkirk makes the runner in the lane as time expires in the first half as Indiana leads Ohio State by a wide margin.
videos.headline: Indiana caps off dominant first half with buzzer beater

videos.description: Trevor Thompson makes the strong layup after being fouled and then completes the 3-point play for Ohio State against Indiana.
videos.headline: Ohio State cuts into lead  with and-1 layup

videos.description: Josh Newkirk comes up with the steal and finishes the and-1 layup on the fast break for Indiana.
videos.headline: Indiana's Newkirk goes coast to coast

videos.description: Marc Loving demands the ball in transition and makes the 3-pointer to get Ohio State back in the game against Indiana.
videos.headline: Ohio State's Loving gets the Buckeyes back in it

videos.description: Thad Matta can't help but smile at a foul call that went against Ohio State.
videos.headline: Ohio State's Matta can't believe  foul call
